Muloñadi kuloñesha kwaNzambi chikwadimena ?
Bayibolu yamwekeshaña ñahi nawu wejima wetu twawanina wanyi ?
Twatela kumona ñahi yiluwa yetu niyawakwetu ?
Bayibolu yahosheleñahu dehi nawudi hakuvula kwawantu jaYehova ?
Ambuña aYehova anamwekeshi ñahi kukeña ?
( Tañenu Mika 4 : 1 , 3 . )
Chumichi chinayikwashi kubula kwikala “ namuloña wamashi awantu ejima . ” — Yililu 20 : 26 .
Muloñadi kuvula kwawantu jaYehova chikunekalili kwakuhayamisha ?
Muloñadi amanakwetu chiyanateli kutuneñeshelawu mpinji yikwawu ?
( Tañenu Aroma 5 : 12 , 19 . )
Neyi mwadiña muIsarela mumufuku aEli nanyanindi , mwadi kwila ñahi ?
Nshidinyi yakoñeliyi Davidi , nawa Nzambi welili ñahi ?
( a ) Kapostolu Petulu wakañenyi ñahi kwila mwahosheliyi ?
( b ) Muloñadi Yehova chatwalekelihu kumuzatisha Petulu nihanyima yakuluwañesha ?
Yesu welili ñahi nayiluwa yaYudasi Isakaroti niPetulu ?
Bayibolu yahosheli nawudi kutalisha hadi ambuña aYehova munanu mafuku ?
Twatela kumona ñahi yiluwa yamanakwetu niahela ?
13 , 14 . ( a ) Muloñadi wutwatela kwikalila adiwunjika kudi wumu namukwawu ?
( b ) Mazwinyi itwatela kwanukaña ?
Yesu wahosheli nindi twatela kwiladi neyi akwetu analuwañeshi ?
Munakukeña kwiladi neyi akwenu ayila katama ?
( Tañenu Matewu 5 : 23 , 24 . )
Kashinshi kawu kayili mumenji ?
Ichi chikuma achishimuna muBayibolu kutalisha hakashinshi nimaana .
Yishimu 3 : 13 - 15 yahosha nawu : “ Muntu wukuwana maana nimuntu wukuheta kashinshi nakooleki . Kuyilandulula yiwukudiilamu yikubadika yiwadyaña hakulandulula siliva , yiwukumwenamu yikubadika wuru wawuwahi .
Wuseya wamaana wabadika wamarubi , yuma yejima yiwakeña hiyesekana nindiku . ”
Hanu dinu , indi kashinshi ?
Chineli nadiña mukulumpi wamudimu , nayileña nakuditeja namukwakutambula nyisonku kuhitila mukumwinka majika kanwa kulonda abuli kwiluka wukombi wadiña hakampani .
Chafuminimu , ijina dami datamini muloña wakubula kwikala washinshika .
Anyanami akwimbujola chakutalilahu chami chachiwahi nawa nashikilimu kuzata nyidimu muchipompelu .
Akwakutambula nyisonku niantu amakwawu inazataña nawu bizinisi añiluka nawu nidi muntu washinshika . ”
Luti wayili kuIsarela , kwadiña nakudifukulayi kudi Nzambi walala .
